These scripts setup and run software on your Raspberry Pi running Raspbian that help it operate an ROV.
They are meant to be used in conjunction with Monterey (github.com/rovsuite/monterey).
Written by Chris Konstad <chriskon149@gmail.com> (7/16/2013)

Released under the MIT License.

To install, simply copy all of the scripts to the home directory of the user "pi", then run setupscript.sh.  It will do the rest of the work.  An internet connection is required.
